content: Ed-Marcavage: Merged two significant PRs this month, with the most substantial being #1343 which added agentic JSDoc generation (+94,056/-84,839 lines). Also merged PR #1547 to fix a JSDoc automation build issue and parametrize PR branch targeting (+261/-179 lines). Made extensive code changes across 1,440 files with a total of +100,348/-85,180 lines, showing sporadic activity concentrated on a few days this month.
